      "acceptanceCriteria": "Software version control, regression testing suite, and documented QA plan must meet Gradation 4 requirements for Class III device submission.",
      "rationale": "QA documentation covers version control and unit testing. Regression test suite exists but covers only 60% of solver pathways. Gradation 4 requires full pathway coverage; achieved level is 3."
