      "acceptanceCriteria": "Experimental boundary conditions must be measured and applied to the CFD model with documented uncertainty.",
      "rationale": "Inlet flow rates and rotational speeds measured with calibrated instruments. Boundary condition uncertainty propagated into CFD inputs. Required level met."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
