      "acceptanceCriteria": "Quantitative agreement metric (e.g., E_rms) must be computed for hemolysis index predictions against experimental data, with statistical confidence intervals, across all 5 operating points.",
      "rationale": "Hemolysis index predictions compared qualitatively at 3 of 5 operating points. No statistical confidence intervals provided. E_rms computed only for velocity fields, not for hemolysis index. Significant gap from required level 5."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Relevance of the quantities of interest",
