      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Validation experiments must replicate VAD operating conditions including hematocrit, blood analog rheology, and rotor speed range matching clinical deployment envelope.",
      "rationale": "Validation performed using water-glycerol analog at 37% hematocrit equivalent. Clinical VAD operates at 38–45% hematocrit. Rotor speed range partially overlaps; two highest clinical speeds not covered by validation experiments."
