      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 5,
      "achievedLevel": 3,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Justification of turbulence model selection, hemolysis power-law model constants, and non-Newtonian rheology model must be provided with sensitivity analysis.",
      "rationale": "SST k-omega turbulence model selected based on prior pump literature. Hemolysis model constants taken from Giersiepen et al. without recalibration. Non-Newtonian effects assumed negligible without sensitivity study. Achieved level 3."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
