      "requiredLevel": 4,
      "achievedLevel": 3,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "All model inputs must be characterized with uncertainty bounds; Monte Carlo propagation must cover hemolysis model constants and fluid properties.",
      "rationale": "Monte Carlo analysis performed on inlet flow rate and rotational speed. Hemolysis model constants treated as fixed; their uncertainty not propagated. Fluid viscosity uncertainty included. Achieved level 3."
