    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "The assessment team concludes that the overall credibility evidence, taken in aggregate, supports a Medium assurance level. While several individual factors fall below required levels, the Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification and the partial validation against FDA pump benchmark data are considered sufficient to support regulatory submission. The team judges the remaining gaps to be manageable through post-market surveillance commitments.",
